<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .otp-container {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #4a6ee0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
    </div>
    
    <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for registering with our Performance Tracking System. To complete your registration, please verify your email address using the following One-Time Password (OTP):</p>
    
    <div class="otp-container">
      <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <p>This OTP will expire in {{expiresIn}} minutes. If you did not request this verification, please ignore this email.</p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Performance Tracking Team</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Performance Tracking System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 